movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: the movie was TOTALLy AWESOME
review: I can't express my feelings right now, I'm so high on TPM.... it totally rocked, I wasn't expecting the very first screen to be a long time ago.....The special effects were very awesome.Don't care what the critics say... GO to the movie, if you're any type of fan to star wars.... this was a Good movie, didn't seem that long either...the last fight scene ROCKED!
